  lines:
  - speakerName: Iroha
    avatar: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8293de3f1bb94bf4baf3a7d5cd3aff72, type: 3}
    content: Oh, no... Kaguya, I'm so sorry. They look... awful.
  - speakerName: Kaguya
    avatar: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 5a472bed8c925d54c88c9848f2e0dd82, type: 3}
    content: (Pokes it with a fork.) Hmm. It's... very sturdy.
  - speakerName: Kaguya
    avatar: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 5a472bed8c925d54c88c9848f2e0dd82, type: 3}
    content: Don't worry, Iroha. Its true calling might be as a doorstop, not a meal.
  - speakerName: Iroha
    avatar: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8293de3f1bb94bf4baf3a7d5cd3aff72, type: 3}
    content: K-Kaguya...! (blushes)
  - speakerName: Kaguya
    avatar: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 5a472bed8c925d54c88c9848f2e0dd82, type: 3}
    content: Your effort was what mattered. Now, let's go find some instant noodles.
